84
00:04:55.980 --> 00:04:59.010
for estrogen receptor-positive breast cancer.

85
00:04:59.370 --> 00:05:02.800
That's 60% of breast cancers that exist out there.

86
00:05:02.840 --> 00:05:06.420
That same year, end of 2014, came Ben

87
00:05:06.500 --> 00:05:10.480
Ebert's now classic paper on somatic

88
00:05:10.520 --> 00:05:14.100
mutations in the form of CHIP or clonal hematopoiesis,

89
00:05:14.820 --> 00:05:18.210
that we have known for many years is a risk factor for

