00:06:01.020 --> 00:06:04.860
never see in cardiovascular trials, and this in part

103
00:06:04.920 --> 00:06:08.840
may be because of the cancer effects but other disease effects.

104
00:06:09.440 --> 00:06:13.140
There were a series of papers that came out, and here I'm going to

105
00:06:13.160 --> 00:06:16.560
embarrass Katherine Moore and Nick Leeper a little bit

106
00:06:17.100 --> 00:06:20.440
about this idea of reverse cardio-oncology.

107
00:06:20.480 --> 00:06:23.920
The fact that cardiovascular disease itself

108
00:06:25.140 --> 00:06:28.660
