00:06:38.600 --> 00:06:42.220
The last thing I want to bring up, and that's when I get off the

114
00:06:42.340 --> 00:06:46.300
stage, is this idea that there are common risk

115
00:06:46.320 --> 00:06:49.820
factors or how cancer

