00:06:50.000 --> 00:06:53.720
affects the heart or heart affects the cancer is critically

117
00:06:53.760 --> 00:06:57.700
important for all of us, right? The number one and the number

118
00:06:57.820 --> 00:07:01.420
two cause of death by far, at least in the US, is

119
00:07:01.460 --> 00:07:03.100
cardiovascular disease and cancer.

120
00:07:03.200 --> 00:07:06.140
Number three is far behind those two.

121
00:07:06.740 --> 00:07:10.660
We have about 700,000 Americans every year

122
00:07:11.080 --> 00:07:12.940
that die of cardiovascular disease.

