131
00:07:40.880 --> 00:07:41.840
In the US,

132
00:07:42.720 --> 00:07:46.580
because of the advent of new therapies in oncology, this whole meeting

133
00:07:46.620 --> 00:07:50.160
is based on that. We have a growing number of cancer

134
00:07:50.260 --> 00:07:54.120
survivors. We have 20 million Americans now who are cancer

135
00:07:54.200 --> 00:07:57.500
survivors. That's 6% of the population.

136
00:07:58.120 --> 00:07:58.840
We have

