161
00:09:31.380 --> 00:09:35.200
And one concept that we introduced is this ABCDE

162
00:09:35.400 --> 00:09:38.840
steps of cardiovascular health. If you look at this

163
00:09:38.900 --> 00:09:42.660
closely, a lot of these are classic cardiovascular risk

164
00:09:42.740 --> 00:09:45.520
factors that we always think about treating.

165
00:09:46.020 --> 00:09:49.920
But if you think about this concept I introduced, that some of these risk

166
00:09:50.020 --> 00:09:53.880
factors like cholesterol, like diet, like diabetes, like

167
00:09:53.960 --> 00:09:55.880
exercise, if you

168
00:09:56.720 --> 00:10:00.380
are not only drivers for cardiac disease but also cancer,

